### 월별 식자재 지출 분석
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/statistics/monthly?yearMonth=2026-01
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 식자재별 비용 비중
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/statistics/ingreient
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 폐기 식자재 비용 분석
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/statistics/disposal
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 페기 식자재 비용 분석(기간별)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/statistics/disposal?startDate=2026-01&endDate=2026-03
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 카테고리별 지출 분석
